text: Laurence Mosely (born May 10, 1933) is an American former sports shooter. He competed in the 25 metre pistol event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:American male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of the United States Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Brooklyn
